[SN]TITLE[SN]
Blame parents not TV, says Teletubbies creator

[SN]FIRST-SENTENCE[SN]
Anne Wood, creator of children's television series In The Night Garden and the Teletubbies, believes TV is often blamed wrongly for children's inability to express themselves.

[SN]RESTBODY[SN]
2 October 2011 Last updated at 08:30 BST
She told Kirsty Young that, without TV, some children would have very little mental stimulation at home.
